# cells-dm-global-apis-accounts

Manages requests related to Accounts.

Example:
```html
<cells-dm-global-apis-accounts
  account-id="[[accountId]]"
  accounts="{{accounts}}"
  account="{{account}}"
  transactions="{{transactions}}"
  indicators="{{indicators}}"
  customized-formats="{{customizedFormats}}"></cells-dm-global-apis-accounts>
```
